 term sources to determine which section offers the best source of expansion
 terms, e.g., are the claims words of particularly high value as expansion
 terms? Note that we consider that there is no interest to use the title
 as source for the expansion since there are only few terms that we can
 collect from the title field in the PRF set.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Itemize

\series bold
Relevance model:
\series default
 For initial retrieval of documents in the 
\emph on
pseudo-relevant
