\begin_inset CommandInset citation
LatexCommand cite
key "Magdy2011"

\end_inset

) as a source of expansion, gave poor performance (see IPC Codes and SynSet
 bars along the Figures).
 
\end_layout

\begin_layout Enumerate
Finally, regarding the best term selection method, we conclude that in general,
 MMRQE provides the best performance, followed by RocchioQE.
